{"title": "King Solomon's Mines", "description": "King Solomon\u2019s Mines, first published in 1885, was a best-selling novel by the Victorian adventure writer H. Rider Haggard. It relates a journey into the heart of Africa by a group of adventurers led by Allan Quatermain in search of the legendary wealth said to be concealed in the mines of the novel\u2019s title. It is significant as the first fictional adventure novel set in Africa, and is considered the genesis of the Lost World literary genre. - Haggard wrote over 50 books, among which were 14 novels starring Allan Quatermain.\n(Summary by Wikipedia/John Nicholson)", "duration": 35471, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "171", "name": "H. Rider Haggard"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/king_solomon_librivox/King_Solomons_Mines_1006.jpg", "copyright_year": "1885", "genres": ["Action & Adventure Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "John Nicholson"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "John Nicholson"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Gesine"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Chapter 01", "readers": [359], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/king_solomon_librivox/kingsolomonsmines_01_haggard_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1694}, {"section": 2, "title": "Chapter 02", "readers": [359], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/king_solomon_librivox/kingsolomonsmines_02_haggard_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1387}, {"section": 3, "title": "Chapter 03", "readers": [359], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/king_solomon_librivox/kingsolomonsmines_03_haggard_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1810}, {"section": 4, "title": "Chapter 04", "readers": [359], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/king_solomon_librivox/kingsolomonsmines_04_haggard_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1470}, {"section": 5, "title": "Chapter 05", "readers": [359], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/king_solomon_librivox/kingsolomonsmines_05_haggard_64kb.mp3", "duration": 2050}, {"section": 6, "title": "Chapter